sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant TauCli as tau_coding.cli
    participant TuiOrPrint as TUI or print renderer
    participant CodingSession
    participant Harness as AgentHarness
    participant AgentLoop as run_agent_loop
    participant Provider as ModelProvider
    participant Tool as AgentTool
    participant Store as JsonlSessionStorage

    User->>TauCli: tau prompt or tau -p prompt
    TauCli->>CodingSession: load session with provider, model, cwd, tools
    CodingSession->>Harness: prompt or continue
    Harness->>AgentLoop: run with transcript and queues
    AgentLoop->>Provider: stream_response
    Provider-->>AgentLoop: provider events
    AgentLoop-->>Harness: message and thinking events
    Harness-->>CodingSession: agent events
    CodingSession->>Store: append completed messages on MessageEndEvent
    AgentLoop->>Tool: execute requested tool calls
    Tool-->>AgentLoop: AgentToolResult
    AgentLoop-->>Harness: tool execution events
    Harness-->>CodingSession: final events
    CodingSession-->>TuiOrPrint: render or project state
    TuiOrPrint-->>User: transcript, status, tool output
